WEBVTT

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:03.189
Hey, good morning, family. Praise the Lord.

00:00:03.199 --> 00:00:05.110
I'm glad you all joined me again today

00:00:05.120 --> 00:00:07.550
to pray. We have a lot of work to do,

00:00:07.560 --> 00:00:09.549
but I just want

00:00:09.559 --> 00:00:12.430
to give you all a testimony real quick

00:00:12.440 --> 00:00:15.310
about a lady who asked for prayer.

00:00:15.320 --> 00:00:17.029
She reached out to us and said she

00:00:17.039 --> 00:00:19.109
broke four ribs. I prayed for her on

00:00:19.119 --> 00:00:21.910
this video, and she was

00:00:21.920 --> 00:00:26.630
in a lot of pain with a broken hip

00:00:26.640 --> 00:00:28.950
