00:00:36.559 --> 00:00:39.470
praying and believing for my healing, I

00:00:39.480 --> 00:00:41.110
just want to let you know the Lord

00:00:41.120 --> 00:00:44.510
healed me."I just want to give

00:00:44.520 --> 00:00:46.869
all the glory, honor, and praise to the

00:00:46.879 --> 00:00:49.990
Lord Jesus Christ. He is the Healer,

00:00:50.000 --> 00:00:53.189
healing the sick the same yesterday,

00:00:53.199 --> 00:00:56.029
today, and forever. He is a good God

00:00:56.039 --> 00:00:57.990
and a Healer. That’s why I have

00:00:58.000 --> 00:01:00.389
this shirt here; I want this to stand

00:01:00.399 --> 00:01:02.549
bold in black and white:

00:01:02.559 --> 00:01:04.390
"Jesus the

00:01:04.390 --> 00:01:04.400
Healer."He

00:01:04.400 --> 00:01:07.270
is a Healer and he is still

00:01:07.280 --> 00:01:10.070
healing the sick today.

00:01:10.070 --> 00:01:10.080
I’m

00:01:10.080 --> 00:01:12.230
bold

00:01:12.240 --> 00:01:13.910
