00:01:16.320 --> 00:01:18.749
We are

00:01:18.759 --> 00:01:21.469
healed; we have to take it by faith.

00:01:21.469 --> 00:01:21.479
You’ve

00:01:21.479 --> 00:01:23.429
got to reach out and grab the hem

00:01:23.439 --> 00:01:25.870
