00:01:30.079 --> 00:01:32.069
wanted to give God praise and

00:01:32.079 --> 00:01:34.910
a testimony that

00:01:34.920 --> 00:01:36.990
He is doing miracles through this

00:01:37.000 --> 00:01:39.310
YouTube channel. I’m believing for

00:01:39.320 --> 00:01:40.990
your manifestation.

00:01:40.990 --> 00:01:41.000
There’s

00:01:41.000 --> 00:01:43.270
